pdgm.pdgmnote: BinyamSisay2008 p. 48. Third-pers persal pronouns are employed together with the above demonstratives in order to form demonstrative pronouns.:This paradigm gives the dem element ha nearSpeaker.

BinyamSisay2008 p. 48. Demonstrative pronouns in Koorete are composed of demonstrative adjectives and third-pers pronouns (Hayward 1982;Binyam 2002). According to Binyam (2002),Koorete has five demonstratives. The choice of the demonstratives is determined by the location and nearness of the referred item with respect to the speaker or hearer and its visibility.
